{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this top down bullet hell with endless zombies, survive as long as you can against a perpetually overwhelming zombie horde. Luckily, you can find an arsenal of high-powered weaponry to help you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/smzchaos.gif?t=1737056076\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game consists of a variety of weapons and characters across all runs, with maps &amp; power-up builds used to differentiate each run. Save humanity and see how long you can live against the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/smzhumans.gif?t=1737056076\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>GPU-Driven technology allowing an impressive sum of zombies on-screen while keeping the frame-rate smooth</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>VR and desktop support</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Progression both in and out of runs</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Level-up your run by buying &amp; upgrading power-ups at the shop</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Collect coins by destroying the horde and saving humans</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Quick Sessions: Unlimited time-length with fast-paced ramp-up</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867890/extras/librarylogo.png?t=1737056076\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Assault Rifle Kills I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2867890/8d6451fc80ed2a9daf1ccb2e6f570c4835b3